    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Suy ra $d(O, (SAB)) = \\frac{1}{2}d(C, (SAB)) = \\frac{1}{2} \\cdot \\frac{\\sqrt{6}}{2} = \\frac{\\sqrt{6}}{4}$."
