  {
    "bbox": [
      203,
      1865,
      1311,
      1906
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Ta có $SO \\perp (ABCD) \\Rightarrow SO \\perp AB$. Mà $AB \\perp ON$ nên suy ra $AB \\perp (SON)$."
